reviewText: Great DVD from some of the best instructors of the time. Good techniques and demonstrated from different angles and speed. Good reference material for  a practicing martial artist. Always learn in a dojo, suplement with DVDs and seminars.

The video quality was very clear. The techniques were awesome and helped me with my techniques and how I should move and flow. I would definitely recommend this DVD to anyone from Beginners to Advanced JuJutsuka.
